Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveThe cover page of the defunct newspaper, Daily Sketch, reporting the coronation of Oba Lamidi Adeyemi III as the Alaafin of Oyo in January 1971, has been trending.
Photo of the newspaper front page went viral as social media users paid tributes to the late first class monarch.
Oba Adeyemi died on Friday and has since been buried.
